saving face is a 2012 documentary film directed by sharmeen obaid-chinoy and daniel junge about acid attacks on women in pakistan .   the film won an emmy award and the 2012 academy award for best documentary short subject , making its director , sharmeen obaid-chinoy , pakistan 's first oscar winner .   the film was inspired from the life of acid victim fakhra younus , who committed suicide in 2012 .